data.title: Greg Kinnear Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Greg Kinnear on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Greg Kinnear including Robots, You've Got Mail, and more.
data.text:
Me? Jealous?

Phil is so preoccupied with impressing his new business partner, Tad (Greg Kinnear), that he doesn't notice what Claire believes is Tad being overtly inappropriate with her. Meanwhile, Jay and Gloria let Mitchell and Cameron stay over while their house is fumigated, and it turns out four is a crowd.

The One With Ross's Grant

Rachel and Monica fight over who will receive an ugly painting from Phoebe's apartment when Mike wants her to get rid of it. Chandler gets on Joey's bad side when he lies about watching Joey's audition tape. Ross is up for a big grant, although Charlie's ex-boyfriend is in charge of who gets it. Dr. Hobart tries to trade--Ross breaks up with Charlie and he'll get the grant. Eventually, Charlie and Dr. Hobart reconcile after he reveals his feelings for her.

Grouch Messing Machine

Elmo and Leela are doing laundry when suddenly the machine goes haywire! It spews water and clothes everywhere - it's clothing chaos! Leela wants to get rid of the machine, but Elmo insists they try to save it. Surely there must someone on Sesame Street who would appreciate a machine that creates a big mess?!
